Determine dependencies from the design flow and generate a Makefile.

This set of scripts automatically determines the dependencies of all files
in the design flow and generates a Makefile.

Usage:
 1) cd to the base chip directory of the design
 2) execute depends-trace.sh
 3) execute depends-eval.sh

depends-trace.sh executes *most* steps of the design flow for all example
applications and all cells as well as for the generation of the
reconfigurable module. All file accesses are traced with "strace".

depends-eval.sh evaluates the traces and generates a (large) Makefile.

